brand new case.  The case does not have the provision for the thermostat
bracket so at the time I didn't install one.  Figure since my case didn't
have one they must not be running thermostats down in Brazil, Mexico, or
where ever they are/were selling new "old style" Beetles at the time.  All
the places they were still selling the Type 1 Beetle generally have a hot
climate...I live in Florida so my thinking at the time was that I would be
okay if I just let it warm up a little before heading out.  Engine runs fine
but I'm going to be pulling it this week for some other work and was having
some second thoughts on the thermostat and was thinking about putting one
in.  Any opinions?  (Ha, like bus folks don't have opinions on engines!)

